dataset_id: High Mountain Asia Landslide Catalog V001
title: High Mountain Asia Landslide Catalog V001
summary: This data set is an open global landslide inventory with input from citizen scientists. The data include the time and location of various landslide events, as well as event characteristics, such as triggers, the number of fatalities, country of occurrence, and the length and area of the slide.
